lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur and Arsenal have the perfect opportunity to bounce back immediately from disappointing midweek defeats when they meet in the most significant North London derby for years at White Hart Lane on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Title Chase Adds Spice to Spurs-Arsenal Clash
